<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <title>AmicBridge – Loans and Investments within a Trusted Network</title>
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1" />
  <meta name="description" content="AmicBridge provides loans and investment opportunities within a private, trust-based network. Private people can lend money to others through written agreements and clear contracts." />
  <meta name="color-scheme" content="light" />

  <style>
    :root {
      --primary: #1f4f8f;
      --primary-light: #e4edf8;
      --background: #f5f5f7;
      --surface: #ffffff;
      --text: #111827;
      --muted: #6b7280;
      --border: #d1d5db;
      --danger: #b91c1c;
      --radius-card: 10px;
    }

    * {
      box-sizing: border-box;
    }

    html {
      scroll-behavior: smooth;
    }

    body {
      margin: 0;
      font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, "Segoe UI", Roboto, sans-serif;
      background: var(--background);
      color: var(--text);
      line-height: 1.6;
    }

    a {
      color: inherit;
      text-decoration: none;
    }

    a:focus-visible,
    button:focus-visible {
      outline: 2px solid var(--primary);
      outline-offset: 2px;
    }

    /* Layout */

    header {
      background: #ffffff;
      border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
    }

    .header-inner {
      max-width: 1040px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 12px 20px;
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 12px;
    }

    .brand {
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: 2px;
    }

    .logo {
      font-size: 20px;
      font-weight: 700;
      letter-spacing: 0.08em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      color: var(--primary);
    }

    .logo span {
      color: #111827;
    }

    .brand-subtitle {
      font-size: 13px;
      color: var(--muted);
    }

    nav {
      display: flex;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      gap: 8px;
      font-size: 14px;
    }

    nav a {
      padding: 6px 10px;
      border-radius: 999px;
      color: var(--muted);
    }

    nav a:hover {
      background: var(--primary-light);
      color: var(--primary);
    }

    .nav-cta {
      border: 1px solid var(--primary);
      color: var(--primary);
      font-weight: 500;
    }

    main {
      max-width: 1040px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 24px 20px 40px;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: 20px;
    }

    /* Hero */

    .hero {
      background: var(--surface);
      border-radius: var(--radius-card);
      border: 1px solid var(--border);
      padding: 24px 22px;
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: minmax(0, 3fr) minmax(260px, 2fr);
      gap: 20px;
      align-items: center;
    }

    .hero-tag {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      border-radius: 999px;
      padding: 4px 10px;
      background: var(--primary-light);
      color: var(--primary);
      font-size: 12px;
      font-weight: 500;
      margin-bottom: 10px;
    }

    .hero h1 {
      margin: 0 0 8px;
      font-size: 28px;
    }

    .hero-subtitle {
      margin: 0 0 14px;
      color: var(--muted);
      font-size: 15px;
      max-width: 600px;
    }

    .hero-cta {
      display: flex;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      gap: 10px;
      margin-bottom: 12px;
    }

    .btn-primary,
    .btn-secondary {
      border-radius: 999px;
      padding: 8px 16px;
      font-size: 14px;
      border: 1px solid transparent;
      cursor: pointer;
      text-decoration: none;
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
    }

    .btn-primary {
      background: var(--primary);
      color: #ffffff;
      border-color: var(--primary);
    }

    .btn-primary:hover {
      background: #163a65;
      border-color: #163a65;
    }

    .btn-secondary {
      background: #ffffff;
      color: var(--primary);
      border-color: var(--primary);
    }

    .btn-secondary:hover {
      background: var(--primary-light);
    }

    .hero-note {
      font-size: 13px;
      color: var(--muted);
    }

    .hero-side {
      border-left: 1px solid var(--border);
      padding-left: 18px;
    }

    .hero-side h2 {
      margin: 0 0 8px;
      font-size: 16px;
    }

    .hero-side p {
      margin: 0 0 10px;
      font-size: 14px;
      color: var(--muted);
    }

    .hero-list {
      list-style: none;
      padding: 0;
      margin: 0;
      font-size: 13px;
      color: var(--muted);
    }

    .hero-list li {
      display: flex;
      gap: 8px;
      margin-bottom: 6px;
    }

    .hero-bullet {
      margin-top: 6px;
      width: 5px;
      height: 5px;
      border-radius: 999px;
      background: var(--primary);
    }

    /* Sections */

    section {
      background: var(--surface);
      border-radius: var(--radius-card);
      border: 1px solid var(--border);
      padding: 18px 18px 20px;
    }

    section h2 {
      margin: 0 0 8px;
      font-size: 20px;
    }

    .section-lead {
      margin: 0 0 10px;
      font-size: 14px;
      color: var(--muted);
    }

    .grid-3 {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(3, minmax(0, 1fr));
      gap: 12px;
      margin-top: 10px;
    }

    .grid-2 {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(2, minmax(0, 1fr));
      gap: 12px;
      margin-top: 10px;
    }

    .card-simple {
      border-radius: 8px;
      border: 1px solid var(--border);
      background: #fafafa;
      padding: 10px 11px;
      font-size: 14px;
    }

    .card-simple h3 {
      margin: 0 0 6px;
      font-size: 15px;
    }

    .card-simple p {
      margin: 0;
      font-size: 13px;
      color: var(--muted);
    }

    .list-clean {
      list-style: none;
      padding: 0;
      margin: 8px 0 0;
      font-size: 14px;
      color: var(--muted);
    }

    .list-clean li {
      display: flex;
      gap: 8px;
      margin-bottom: 6px;
    }

    .list-bullet {
      margin-top: 6px;
      width: 6px;
      height: 6px;
      border-radius: 999px;
      background: #9ca3af;
    }

    .note-small {
      font-size: 12px;
      color: var(--muted);
      margin-top: 8px;
    }

    /* Contact */

    .contact-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: minmax(0, 1.2fr) minmax(0, 1.8fr);
      gap: 14px;
      margin-top: 10px;
      font-size: 14px;
    }

    .contact-card {
      border-radius: 8px;
      border: 1px solid var(--border);
      background: #fafafa;
      padding: 10px 11px;
    }

    .contact-card h3 {
      margin: 0 0 6px;
      font-size: 15px;
    }

    .contact-field-label {
      font-size: 12px;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: 0.08em;
      color: var(--muted);
    }

    .contact-field-value {
      font-size: 14px;
      margin-bottom: 6px;
    }

    footer {
      border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
      background: #ffffff;
      padding: 14px 20px 20px;
      font-size: 13px;
      color: var(--muted);
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 4px;
    }

    /* Responsive */

    @media (max-width: 900px) {
      .hero {
        grid-template-columns: minmax(0, 1fr);
      }

      .hero-side {
        border-left: none;
        border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
        padding-left: 0;
        padding-top: 14px;
        margin-top: 6px;
      }

      .grid-3 {
        grid-template-columns: minmax(0, 1fr);
      }

      .grid-2 {
        grid-template-columns: minmax(0, 1fr);
      }

      .contact-grid {
        grid-template-columns: minmax(0, 1fr);
      }
    }

    @media (max-width: 640px) {
      .header-inner {
        flex-direction: column;
        align-items: flex-start;
      }

      nav {
        justify-content: flex-start;
      }

      main {
        padding-inline: 14px;
      }
    }
  </style>
</head>

<body>
<header>
  <div class="header-inner">
    <div class="brand">
      <div class="logo">AMIC<span>BRIDGE</span></div>
      <div class="brand-subtitle">Loans and investments within a trusted private network</div>
    </div>

    <nav aria-label="Main navigation">
      <a href="#products">Products</a>
      <a href="#how">How it works</a>
      <a href="#who">Who we serve</a>
      <a href="#safety">Safety & contracts</a>
      <a href="#contact" class="nav-cta">Contact</a>
    </nav>
  </div>
</header>

<main>
  <!-- HERO -->
  <section class="hero" aria-labelledby="hero-title">
    <div>
      <div class="hero-tag">Trust before money</div>
      <h1 id="hero-title">Loans and investments through the AmicBridge network.</h1>

      <p class="hero-subtitle">
        AmicBridge connects people who know and trust each other. We help structure
        loans and investment agreements between private people and businesses – with clear
        contracts, repayment plans and expectations on both sides.
      </p>

      <div class="hero-cta">
        <a href="#contact" class="btn-primary">Talk to us</a>
        <a href="#products" class="btn-secondary">See our products</a>
      </div>

      <p class="hero-note">
        AmicBridge is a structured private network, not a public anonymous lending platform.
      </p>
    </div>

    <aside class="hero-side" aria-label="Key points">
      <h2>What AmicBridge focuses on</h2>
      <p>
        We combine a trusted private network with written contracts and simple,
        transparent loan and investment structures.
      </p>
      <ul class="hero-list">
        <li>
          <span class="hero-bullet"></span>
          <span>Loans arranged inside a known, vetted network.</span>
        </li>
        <li>
          <span class="hero-bullet"></span>
          <span>Private people can lend their money to others through clear agreements.</span>
        </li>
        <li>
          <span class="hero-bullet"></span>
          <span>Written contracts, clear interest and repayment terms.</span>
        </li>
        <li>
          <span class="hero-bullet"></span>
          <span>No hidden fees, no unclear conditions.</span>
        </li>
      </ul>
    </aside>
  </section>

  <!-- PRODUCTS -->
  <section id="products" aria-labelledby="products-title">
    <h2 id="products-title">Products and services</h2>
    <p class="section-lead">
      We help structure and follow up financial agreements inside the AmicBridge network.
      All products are based on written contracts and clear terms.
    </p>

    <div class="grid-3">
      <div class="card-simple">
        <h3>Personal loans</h3>
        <p>
          Loans between private people arranged inside the AmicBridge network. Agreements
          define amount, interest, repayment plan and what happens if payments are delayed.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="card-simple">
        <h3>Private lending as an investor</h3>
        <p>
          Private people with savings can lend money to others in the network.
          We structure the contracts and help set realistic expectations for risk and return.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="card-simple">
        <h3>Simple business funding</h3>
        <p>
          Funding for smaller businesses and projects, backed by people in the network.
          We focus on clear agreements rather than complex financial products.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <p class="note-small">
      Availability of products can depend on local regulation and individual assessment.
    </p>
  </section>

  <!-- HOW IT WORKS -->
  <section id="how" aria-labelledby="how-title">
    <h2 id="how-title">How it works</h2>
    <p class="section-lead">
      Every agreement in AmicBridge follows a simple, structured process.
    </p>

    <div class="grid-4">
      <!-- Use grid-2 with nested cards for clarity -->
      <div class="grid-2">
        <div class="card-simple">
          <h3>1. We match within the network</h3>
          <p>
            A borrower or project is matched with lenders or investors from the AmicBridge
            network – people and businesses that meet our basic criteria.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="card-simple">
          <h3>2. Terms are discussed</h3>
          <p>
            Amount, duration, interest, risk and security are discussed openly.
            We help both sides understand what the agreement means in practice.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="card-simple">
          <h3>3. Contract is written</h3>
          <p>
            A written agreement is created in clear language. Both sides review and confirm
            before any money is transferred.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="card-simple">
          <h3>4. Follow-up and overview</h3>
          <p>
            Payments and obligations are followed up according to the agreement.
            Both parties keep an overview of what has been paid and what is still due.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- WHO WE SERVE + SAFETY -->
  <section id="who" aria-labelledby="who-title">
    <h2 id="who-title">Who we serve</h2>
    <p class="section-lead">
      AmicBridge is for people and businesses who take agreements seriously.
    </p>

    <div class="grid-2">
      <div class="card-simple">
        <h3>Borrowers</h3>
        <ul class="list-clean">
          <li>
            <span class="list-bullet"></span>
            <span>Private people who need a structured loan from someone they trust.</span>
          </li>
          <li>
            <span class="list-bullet"></span>
            <span>Small businesses that want simple funding with clear terms.</span>
          </li>
          <li>
            <span class="list-bullet"></span>
            <span>People who want to avoid unclear private arrangements and conflicts later.</span>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="card-simple" id="safety">
        <h3>Lenders and investors</h3>
        <ul class="list-clean">
          <li>
            <span class="list-bullet"></span>
            <span>Private people who want to lend money with written contracts and follow-up.</span>
          </li>
          <li>
            <span class="list-bullet"></span>
            <span>Individuals who want exposure to real people and projects, not anonymous pools.</span>
          </li>
          <li>
            <span class="list-bullet"></span>
            <span>People who value trust and transparency more than chasing the highest risk.</span>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- SAFETY & CONTRACTS -->
  <section aria-labelledby="safety-title">
    <h2 id="safety-title">Safety, contracts and responsibilities</h2>
    <p class="section-lead">
      Trust is the starting point, but written agreements and clear responsibilities
      are what protect both sides.
    </p>

    <div class="grid-3">
      <div class="card-simple">
        <h3>Written contracts</h3>
        <p>
          Every loan and investment in AmicBridge is based on a written contract.
          The contract describes amounts, interest, timing, security and consequences
          if payments are not made.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="card-simple">
        <h3>Transparent costs</h3>
        <p>
          We aim for simple, understandable costs and interest. There are no hidden
          fees or unexpected conditions in the small print.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="card-simple">
        <h3>Network-based trust</h3>
        <p>
          Agreements happen inside a network where participants are known and
          assessed. This is not a fully open, anonymous marketplace.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <p class="note-small">
      All financial decisions involve risk. We encourage both borrowers and lenders to
      understand their obligations fully before signing an agreement.
    </p>
  </section>

  <!-- CONTACT -->
  <section id="contact" aria-labelledby="contact-title">
    <h2 id="contact-title">Contact AmicBridge</h2>
    <p class="section-lead">
      If you want to use the AmicBridge network for loans or investments, or if you are
      interested in cooperation, you can contact us directly.
    </p>

    <div class="contact-grid">
      <div class="contact-card">
        <h3>Get in touch</h3>
        <div class="contact-field">
          <div class="contact-field-label">Contact person</div>
          <div class="contact-field-value">Your Name Here</div>
        </div>
        <div class="contact-field">
          <div class="contact-field-label">Email</div>
          <div class="contact-field-value">
            <a href="mailto:you@example.com">you@example.com</a>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="contact-field">
          <div class="contact-field-label">Location</div>
          <div class="contact-field-value">Based in Norway</div>
        </div>
        <p class="note-small">
          Replace the placeholder name and email with your real details before publishing.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="contact-card">
        <h3>What to include in your message</h3>
        <ul class="list-clean">
          <li>
            <span class="list-bullet"></span>
            <span>Whether you want to borrow, lend, invest – or cooperate.</span>
          </li>
          <li>
            <span class="list-bullet"></span>
            <span>Where you are based and if you already have a network that might fit AmicBridge.</span>
          </li>
          <li>
            <span class="list-bullet"></span>
            <span>A short description of your experience with loans or investments so far.</span>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</main>

<footer>
  <span>© <span id="year"></span> AmicBridge. All rights reserved.</span>
  <span>AmicBridge is a private network solution for loans and investments. It is not a bank. Products and availability may depend on local regulations.</span>
</footer>

<script>
  // Set current year in footer
  document.getElementById('year').textContent = new Date().getFullYear();
</script>
</body>
</html>
